name: TIDAL UI Kit for Figma
description:
I'm super excited to finally share this UI Kit I made for the TIDAL web application. I always wanted to contribute and give back to the Figma community, and this UI Kit marks my first step towards that goal, I really hope you will find it helpful.


This first release - 0.8, contains only a handful of components, icons and screens. My plan is to constantly push updates and improvements in the long run. For now, you can currently access:


  • 20+ Components
  • 25+ Icons
  • Artwork Template with multiple variants
  • 5+ Screen Templates


Aaand that's pretty much it for now!


If you find this useful or just want to say hi, then make sure to drop by and leave a message! - @vladpustianu
